    "summary": "The user expresses profound dissociation and a loss of identity, describing themselves as a \"ghost in a shell\" and feeling that their \"real self\" is gone. The assistant responds with empathetic validation and consistently suggests seeking professional mental health support or exploring the feelings further.",
